snippet.title: Best VGM 1338 - Far Cry 3 : Blood Dragon - Resurrection
snippet.description:
Soundtrack available on iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/far-cry-3-blood-dragon-original/id636431312

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3 / PC
Far Cry 3 : Blood Dragon (2013)
Resurrection
Power Glove
